1. Created an app for displaying robot data from a RESTful API.
2. Implemented a search screen that allows users to search for robots by name.
3. Integrated GET API calls to retrieve robot data based on user input.
4. Designed the search screen with a Text input field for user queries.
5. Utilized a filter function to match user input with robot names and display filtered results using GridView.builder.
6. Designed a custom widget to display robot details as per the documentation.
7.Customized the BottomNavigationBar to fit the app's design and functionality.
8.Handled the challenge of API responses delivering images in PNG format.
9.Converted PNG data into Uint8List and used the MemoryImage widget to display images in the app.
